{"tid":1821472,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"提提大家,過去12個月內入境過台灣3次,就可以去搞張常客證","createTime":"2020-01-12T10:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T05:29:06.000Z","uid":33359,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"295bed6da348ac2aacdcec2e75c93bedb0da8a3d","tid":1821472,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:15:07.000Z","msg":"去過台北都知<br />\n台北入境條龍最少排半個鐘,多起上黎排成個鐘都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咗常客證你就可以排第兩條龍,個條龍少人好多,5-10分鐘就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要過去12個月內入境過台灣3次,就可以去搞張常客證,張證為期一年,使用次數無限<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df1b7623690f227b8627001aaa4f971b28c861b","tid":1821472,"uid":181997,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:16:03.000Z","msg":"知你叻啦"},{"pid":"8de1735caaaf335d6dacce2d78f432333ae01ce7","tid":1821472,"uid":182145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:18:10.000Z","msg":"點整"},{"pid":"7576273f2aae6c63e2c1c7296e9c26d112441d9e","tid":1821472,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8de1735caaaf335d6dacce2d78f432333ae01ce7","tid":1821472,"uid":182145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:18:10.000Z","msg":"點整"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:19:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://niaspeedy.immigration.gov.tw/qacAction.action\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fniaspeedy.immigration.gov.tw%2FqacAction.action&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXSvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=20acf5f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://niaspeedy.immigration.gov.tw/qacAction.action</a>"},{"pid":"125e15d61fc0cfbb7869fa085ada96dcbbde76a6","tid":1821472,"uid":261332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:20:22.000Z","msg":"點搞架？<br />\n第三次入境果時順便搞埋？<br />\n定係要第三次入境前或後申請？"},{"pid":"7a0de5dcbf49365fe3415d9c876cdad19d4d50a7","tid":1821472,"uid":18214